FIGS. 3A and 3B are plan views of a part of a camera body shown in FIG. 2 to explain an operation of a film winding mechanism;


FIGS. 4A and 4B are a sectional view and a diagram of a bar code sensor, respectively, to explain an operation thereof;


FIG. 5 is a circuit block diagram of an electronic circuit unit;


FIG. 6 is a flow chart of a main operation of a camera according to the present invention;


FIG. 7 is a flow chart of a film loading operation in a camera according to the present invention;


FIGS. 8A, 8B and 8C are sectional views of different examples of a bar code sensor; and


FIG. 9 is a schematic view of a leading end of a 120 film with a bar code.
